import React from 'react'
import { ListGroup, ListGroupItem } from 'reactstrap'

function Menu(){
    return (
        <ListGroup>
            <ListGroupItem tag='a'href='#!'>Home</ListGroupItem>
            <ListGroupItem>Home</ListGroupItem>
            <ListGroupItem>Home</ListGroupItem>
        </ListGroup>)
}

export default Menu
